Cheats
Kill figure - kill any chosen figure, but the king.

Change color of figure - changes color of any chosen figure, but the king.

Set figure - set any chosen figure in the same color as moving player.

Block figure - block any chosen figure for 6 moves (Cheat is also counted as 1 move), (it is counting both white and black moves).

In variants with checkmate you can not make cheat that would allow enemy to capture your king.